# ADWATrial Project Rules

## Core Identity
- **Name:** ADWATrial (Premium Ethiopian Marketplace)
- **Aesthetic:** Luxury Black & Gold. 
- **Palette:** Background: #0A0A0A, Primary Gold: #D4AF37, Text: #F5E6BE, Surface: #1A1A1A.
- **Tone:** Professional, clean, and high-end (Airbnb/Booking.com level).

## Tech Stack Guidelines
- **Framework:** Next.js 15+ (App Router).
- **Styling:** Tailwind CSS v4 (Use @theme variables from globals.css).
- **Components:** shadcn/ui (Vega/Radix).
- **Database:** Prisma with PostgreSQL.
- **Icons:** Lucide React.

## Coding Standards
- Use **Server Components** by default. Only use 'use client' for interactive elements.
- Always use **TypeScript** with strict types. No 'any'.
- Use **Server Actions** for all database mutations.
- Follow a mobile-first responsive design pattern.
- All buttons and interactive gold elements should have a subtle hover glow: `shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(212,175,55,0.3)]`.

## UI/UX Rules
- Use a **Serif font** (Playfair Display) for large headings and a **Sans font** (Geist) for body text.
- Navigation must be sticky with a glassmorphism effect (bg-black/80 backdrop-blur).